Class EventIDService

  • java.lang.Object
    • Service.EventIDService

  • public class EventIDService
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a EventID Service object. Implements Service interface. Instance created by EventIDHandler. Brains of the api call. Verifies Request. Returns the single Event object with the specified ID. Connection between EventIDHandler and DAO classes Service method takes an object that implements "request" as a parameter and returns an object of that implements "result."
